item.title: First Fairbanks Raspberry Jam
item.description:
The first Fairbanks Raspberry Jam is 1:30-3:30 Saturday April 29th, 2017 Downtown Fairbanks at the Fairbanks Economic Development Corporation. Join us and meet other local Raspberry Pi enthusiasts

  • Share your projects
  • Find out what others are doing
  • Learn new stuff
  • Collaborate with others

Sign up and be eligible to win a Pi at the event (must be present to win).

Use our Raspberry Jam GitHub Issue to help us plan further.
